	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=65101"><span id="Scholar">Drienne, Guardian of the Glade</span></a><br /><b><span id="Scholar">Scholar</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">294 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>This isn't a 225 HP heal.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you look at the spell info, it gives 225HP to max HP, but not to current HP.  If you look at the spell info for Brell's Mountainous Barrier, or any of the INT-caster shield spells, you'll see the same.  If you look at buffs such as Virtue and Skin Like Nature, you'll see that both current and max HP are increased.  This also does not stack with Focus.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br /><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76285 target=akztarg>Drienne Gardairne</a> -- 68 Ranger<br/><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=316502 target=akztarg>Xide Kyck</a> -- 65 Necromancer<br/><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=725442 target=akztarg>Hwel Jung</a> -- 65 Rogue</td></tr>
